item.title: How to make my self owner
item.dc:creator: @system system
item.description:
@system wrote:

go on rs2loginprotocol.java
then do CTRL+F and search for his name, (“Josem731”) then delete that name and enter your name instead
then compile the server and run, and there ya go, youre owner.

and also, edit Commands.java if it p.ignorecase, (You could do as above, CTRL+F and search for josem731) and change to your name. ^^

~JoseOwnz

item.title: How to make my self owner
item.dc:creator: @mr_luigi_77 mr luigi 77
item.description:
@mr_luigi_77 wrote:

Characters folder, find your name. (Usually in alphabetical order) and change PlayerRights — to a 3, instead of a 0. Here is all of the numbers and what they mean.

0 = Normal Player 1 = Moderator 2 = Administrator 3 = Owner 4 = Hidden Administrator 10 = Hidden Owner
